data.description: With desirable location + modern updates, this charming 3/3 Bay View duplex has it all! Brick exterior, newer roof (2019), newer windows (2020), new furnaces (2023), new attic insulation (2023), and newer water heaters = low maintenance, all you have to do is move in! Lower unit has been recently updated and features LVP in hallway & kitchen and 2017 carpet (professionally cleaned in Sept) in BRs and LR.  Upper unit has been owner occupied, recently updated with LVP floors throughout the entire apartment. Full basement with storage, per seller foundation is solid and dry. Private back yard, 2 car detached garage with 220V electricity, and 2 car parking slab complete this total package. Perfect for owner occupant or as an investment property! Do not let this one pass you by.
